{
  "texts": [
    "The process of learning to code often involves repetitive practice, debugging, and problem-solving, which can be time-consuming and frustrating for students.",
    "AI tools, such as Chat-GPT, can streamline these processes by offering instant guidance and corrections (Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023a).",
    "This immediate feedback can help students understand their mistakes in real-time, reducing frustration and accelerating the learning process (Daun & Brings, 2023).",
    "However, proper integration of AI tools in learning environments can be crucial to get effective results (Muhie & Woldie, 2020).",
    "To increase the effectiveness of AI-based learning materials, Pesovski et al. (2024) underlines the importance of designing learning materials based on distinct needs of students with different performance levels."
  ]
}